Well, my earliest research is, I deserted the, 
after getting my PhD.

02:43.723 --> 02:56.575
I had problems when I got to this college in 
Oklahoma, so far as the library was concerned, and

02:43.723 --> 02:56.575
I couldn't get together enough library to do 
research in the parasitology area. So I shifted to

02:56.595 --> 03:01.339
the freshwater crustacea, and Some of the best 
work was back there in the early days. With the

03:07.025 --> 03:26.672
freshwater crustacea, I studied cave fauna all 
