03:30.108 --> 03:33.554
because they knew of my work in this area. They 
hired me for a completely different thing.

03:38.943 --> 03:44.132
From what I've been doing, I started with Dr. 
Jekyll and Mr. Hyde. There are two sets of people in

03:45.174 --> 03:48.099
the United States that know me. One of them knows me 
from my work in the crustacean and the freshwater

03:48.620 --> 03:53.989
biology area.

03:56.787 --> 04:00.432
The other knows me from my work in pollution. 
Completely separate.

